<title>
Seat Belt Buckle Inspection
</title>
<servinfosub id = "AENCP70A8106004001">
<title>
Belt Latch
</title>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
It should be securely locked when tongue plate (2) is latched.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Lock should be released by pressing release button (3) when tongue plate (2) is latched to buckle (1).
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAW101810007.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "45.864mm" ver = "01" gw = "117" gh = "114"/>
</figure>
</item>
</list1>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "AENCP70A8106004002">
<title>
Seat Belt Buckle Switch
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Disconnect seat belt buckle switch connector (4).
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Check continuity between terminal 1 and 2 of seat belt buckle switch connector (4).
</ptxt>
</s1>
